:::'''Akmonides:''' *Sigh* Alright, alright, consider it a gesture of friendship. I'll give you this information for free...
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504040612_2-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504040612_2-->
:::'''Akmonides:''' Here, that young man who looks like he might explode at any moment &mdash; his family runs a general store. Their main business is supplying expedition teams with provisions when they head out of the city.
:::'''Akmonides:''' As for that gloomy guy who looks like he hasn't slept in three days, he belongs to a fairly well-known local expedition team. He's actually the younger brother of the team's leader.
:::'''Akmonides:''' A while ago, their squad went out to explore a new area. By sheer bad luck, they ran into the black tide, and the casualties were severe. After barely managing to escape with their lives, they tried to gather themselves and head back to the city, only to find that there was an issue with their supplies.
:::'''Akmonides:''' The backup food was all near expiry and about to spoil, and the medical kits were put together from leftover scraps &mdash; clearly, there was an inside job.
:::'''Akmonides:''' These two guys, in order to investigate, came to the bath to gather information. They found out that "the captain of that expedition made some secret deal with the old shopkeeper some time ago" &mdash; and that's when the argument started~
:::'''Gloomy Teen:''' ...I'll say it one last time. Stop causing trouble. Use your wooden little brain and think carefully about what you actually came here to do.
:::'''Annoyed Youth:''' Am I being unreasonable? Clearly, it's you who's guilty and trying to change the subject! Nice try!
:::'''Akmonides:''' Look at that. These two have grown up together, years of friendship, and yet when something like this happens, it's just like a chimera biting another chimera &mdash; just as messy as a mouthful of fur, haha~
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Ah, that message wasn't from you, was it...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504040621-->
::::'''Akmonides:''' Ah, I just love smart people like you! You think they're a bit noisy too, don't you?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you really not a Masked Fool?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504040623-->
::::'''Akmonides:''' The Masked... Fool? What's that? Sounds intriguing &mdash; could you tell me about it in detail later?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504040624-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504040624-->
:::'''Akmonides:''' I say, you two &mdash; don't you think that's enough? Everyone's staring at you now. Are you sure you want to keep this show going on?
::<pre>{
	"$type": "RPG.GameCore.ActiveVirtualCamera",
	"AreaName": "LevelArea_P10401_F10401001_G357",
	"AnchorName": "Anchor2"
}</pre>
:::'''Annoyed Youth:''' Huh? Weren't you the one who told us &mdash;
:::'''Akmonides:''' Are you questioning the information I provided?
:::'''Gloomy Teen:''' ...That's not what he means. It's just that your "making a secret deal" comment is a bit too vague...
:::'''Akmonides:''' Exactly! Which is why you'll have to figure out the rest yourselves. Or do you expect me to break it all down and explain every detail? That would cost you extra, you know.
:::'''Annoyed Youth:''' You...!
:::'''Akmonides:''' *Sigh* Fine, fine. Since you've worked so hard entertaining everyone here, I'll throw in a freebie &mdash; take a good look at the medical expenses for the expedition team over the past few months. If you're lucky, you might catch a big rock rat.
:::'''Annoyed Youth:''' What? Uncle Libius would never...
:::'''Gloomy Teen:''' I see. Thank you. Let's go, Ifris. We'll talk later if you need.
:::'''Akmonides:''' Thank you for your visit, and we look forward to seeing you again next time~
::<pre>{
	"$type": "RPG.GameCore.ActiveVirtualCamera",
	"AreaName": "LevelArea_P10401_F10401001_G357",
	"AnchorName": "Anchor2",
	"IsActive": false
