:::'''Akmonides:''' Oh, you're finally willing to talk with me about this? I've been waiting for so long that Phagousa is about to wake up.
:::'''Akmonides:''' Okay, so talk to me. What is your home like? And what did you encounter on your road here?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504033079_9-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504033079_9-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Talk about your "home."
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504040708-->
::::'''Akmonides:''' It's hard to imagine that... This Herta, kin to Cerces, possess such power, is capable of building such a large and intricate tower. And to use that as a display of her rare treasures too... I fear this feat is more than comparable to Thalesus' efforts.
::::'''Akmonides:''' Your "Nameless" exploration team... Do they also explore the world on the back of a giant beast? How romantic.
::::'''Akmonides:''' I knew you were interesting, friend. From the moment I first laid eyes on you, I knew we had a special bond.
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Talk about your travels.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504040713-->
::::'''Akmonides:''' ...
::::'''Akmonides:''' How strange. I have never heard of any of these cities you've been to.
::::'''Akmonides:''' Haha, don't be nervous, friend. I don't mean anything. Just feeling a bit emotional.
::::'''Akmonides:''' Look... Though I have a little bit of skill, a little bit more capability than most people here, hearing your story makes me think that my life here is too dull!
::::'''Akmonides:''' I really want to adventure about like you. Want to see what waits beyond the heights of Oronyx, and where the end of the Thanatos' River of Souls lies...
::::'''Akmonides:''' ...Thalassopolis, right?
::::'''Akmonides:''' Is your exploration team still short-handed? How about you bring me with you on the way back? I really want to see that rabbit-like kin of Janus that you mentioned.
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} You remind me of someone familiar.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504040722-->
::::'''Akmonides:''' Haha, then maybe we are long-lost brothers that share a single parent.
::::'''Akmonides:''' Though, that follower of Zagreus you talk of does sound interesting. And that tavern in the city of... Penacony, was it?
::::'''Akmonides:''' You haven't been there either, right? How about next time we both find a way to get in and take a look?
:::{{DIcon|Exit}} That's enough chit-chat for now.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504040727-->
::::'''Akmonides:''' Leaving already? But we haven't talked enough yet...
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I'm busy, so I'll be heading off.
:::'''Akmonides:''' I'll miss you, friend &mdash; so, so much. You'll come back and see me, right?
